Introduction

Aurora is a Chinese singer. She is a former member of the girl group NATURE.

In January 2020, Aurora took part in the Chinese survival show Youth With You 2. Unfortunately, she was eliminated in episode 10, having secured the 65th position in episode 6 and the 109th position in the initial mission of episode 7. The exact ranking at the time of elimination remains undisclosed.

In February 2021, n.CH Entertainment announced that Aurora would be resuming her activities with NATURE, starting from February 23.
